<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="da">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sandnes Double Sunday | Garnstuen.dk</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* --- GLOBAL THEME STYLES --- */
        :root {
            --bg-vellum: #F9F7F2;
            --text-dark: #3E3A35;
            --text-muted: #7A7A7A;
            --gold-accent: rgba(197, 163, 113, 0.6);
            --font-serif: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            --font-sans: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
        }
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { background-color: var(--bg-vellum); color: var(--text-dark); font-family: var(--font-sans); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: flex; flex-direction: column; min-height: 100vh; }
        a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }
        main { flex: 1; }

        /* --- THE PRISTINE HEADER --- */
        header { 
            padding: 20px 5%; 
            display: flex; 
            justify-content: space-between; 
            align-items: center; 
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            background-color: var(--bg-vellum);
        }
        .logo img { max-height: 80px; width: auto; display: block; }
        .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 25px; font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-weight: 500; transition: all 0.3s ease; }
        .nav-links a:hover, .nav-links a.active-link { color: #C5A371; }
        .header-actions { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-weight: 500; }
        .menu-toggle { display: none; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between; width: 25px; height: 18px; cursor: pointer; }
        .menu-toggle span { width: 100%; height: 2px; background-color: var(--text-dark); transition: all 0.3s ease; }

        /* --- BREADCRUMBS --- */
        .breadcrumbs { padding: 30px 5% 0; font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        .breadcrumbs a { transition: color 0.3s; }
        .breadcrumbs a:hover { color: var(--text-dark); }
        .breadcrumbs span { margin: 0 10px; }

        /* --- PRODUCT DETAIL LAYOUT --- */
        .product-container { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; padding: 40px 5% 100px; max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; align-items: start; }
        
        /* Left: Image Gallery */
        .gallery-main { 
            width: 100%; 
            aspect-ratio: 4/5; 
            background-image: url('images/sandnes-sunday-sage.jpg'); /* Replace with actual image */
            background-size: cover; 
            background-position: center; 
            background-color: #849684;
            position: relative;
            clip-path: polygon(5% 0, 95% 0, 100% 5%, 100% 95%, 95% 100%, 5% 100%, 0 95%, 0 5%);
        }
        .gallery-main::after {
            content: ""; position: absolute; inset: 4px; border: 1px solid var(--gold-accent); pointer-events: none;
            clip-path: polygon(5% 0, 95% 0, 100% 5%, 100% 95%, 95% 100%, 5% 100%, 0 95%, 0 5%);
        }
        .gallery-thumbnails { display: flex; gap: 15px; margin-top: 20px; }
        .thumb { width: 80px; aspect-ratio: 1; background-size: cover; background-position: center; cursor: pointer; opacity: 0.6; transition: opacity 0.3s; border: 1px solid transparent; }
        .thumb:hover, .thumb.active { opacity: 1; border-color: var(--gold-accent); }

        /* Right: Product Info */
        .product-info h1 { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 3.2rem; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 5px; line-height: 1.1; }
        .product-brand { font-size: 0.9rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--text-muted); display: block; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .product-price { font-size: 1.5rem; font-family: var(--font-serif); color: var(--text-dark); margin-bottom: 30px; display: block; }
        
        .product-description { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 40px; }
        
        /* Subtle divider */
        .divider-svg { display: block; margin: 30px 0; width: 100px; opacity: 0.5; }

        /* Technical Specs Grid */
        .specs-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px 40px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        .spec-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
        .spec-label { font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .spec-value { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-dark); }

        /* Actions: Quantity and Button */
        .action-row { display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        .quantity-selector { display: flex; align-items: center; border: 1px solid #ddd; height: 55px; }
        .qty-btn { background: none; border: none; padding: 0 20px; font-size: 1.2rem; cursor: pointer; color: var(--text-dark); transition: color 0.3s; }
        .qty-btn:hover { color: #C5A371; }
        .qty-input { width: 50px; text-align: center; border: none; background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 1rem; }
        
        .btn-add { flex: 1; height: 55px; background-color: var(--text-dark); color: white; border: none; font-family: var(--font-sans); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.3s; }
        .btn-add:hover { background-color: #1a1a1a; }

        /* --- THE RICH FOOTER --- */
        footer { background-color: #EFECE6; padding: 80px 5% 40px; margin-top: auto; }
        .footer-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 40px; max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1); padding-bottom: 40px; }
        .footer-col h4 { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 600; }
        .footer-col p, .footer-col ul { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.8; }
        .footer-col ul { list-style: none; }
        .footer-col ul li { margin-bottom: 10px; cursor: pointer; transition: color 0.3s ease; }
        .footer-col ul li:hover { color: var(--text-dark); }
        .footer-icon-text { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .footer-icon-text svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 3px; fill: var(--text-muted); }
        .whatsapp-btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; background-color: #25D366; color: white !important; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 500; margin-top: 15px; transition: background 0.3s; }
        .whatsapp-btn:hover { background-color: #128C7E; }
        .whatsapp-btn svg { fill: white; width: 18px; height: 18px; margin: 0; }
        .map-link { color: var(--text-dark); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--text-dark); padding-bottom: 2px; font-weight: 500; }
        .footer-bottom { text-align: center; padding-top: 30px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); }

        /* Mobile Adjustments */
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            header { justify-content: center; padding: 15px 5%; }
            .header-actions { position: absolute; right: 5%; }
            .header-actions > a { display: none; }
            .logo img { max-height: 75px; }
            .nav-links { position: absolute; top: 100%; left: 0; width: 100%; background-color: var(--bg-vellum); flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 20px; padding: 0; height: 0; overflow: hidden; border-bottom: none; z-index: 999; }
            .nav-links.active { padding: 30px 0; height: auto; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1); box-shadow: 0 10px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
            .menu-toggle { display: flex; }
            
            .product-container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; padding-top: 20px; }
            .product-info h1 { font-size: 2.6rem; }
            .action-row { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
            .quantity-selector { justify-content: space-between; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <a href="index.html" class="logo">
            <img src="images/logo.png" alt="Garnstuen Logo">
        </a>
        <nav class="nav-links" id="nav-menu">
            <a href="yarn.html" class="active-link">Garn</a>
            <a href="needles.html">Strikkepinde & Hæklenåle</a>
            <a href="accessories.html">Tilbehør & Knapper</a>
            <a href="books.html">Bøger & Opskrifter</a>
            <a href="assortment.html">Sortiment</a>
            <a href="reserve.html" style="display: none;" id="mobile-reserve">Reservationer</a>
        </nav>
        <div class="header-actions">
            <a href="reserve.html">Reservationer</a>
            <div class="menu-toggle" id="mobile-toggle">
                <span></span><span></span><span></span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="breadcrumbs">
        <a href="index.html">Forside</a> <span>/</span> <a href="yarn.html">Garn</a> <span>/</span> Double Sunday
    </div>

    <main>
        <div class="product-container">
            <div class="product-gallery">
                <div class="gallery-main"></div>
                <div class="gallery-thumbnails">
                    <div class="thumb active" style="background-image: url('images/sandnes-sunday-sage.jpg'); background-color: #849684;"></div>
                    <div class="thumb" style="background-image: url('images/sandnes-sunday-detail.jpg'); background-color: #A89684;"></div>
                    <div class="thumb" style="background-image: url('images/sandnes-sunday-swatch.jpg'); background-color: #7C7A75;"></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="product-info">
                <span class="product-brand">Sandnes Garn</span>
                <h1>Double Sunday</h1>
                <span class="product-price">DKK 45,00</span>
                
                <p class="product-description">
                    Double Sunday er Sandnes Garns absolutte bestseller. Det er et tykt, ikke-superwash behandlet merinogarn, som giver et utrolig smukt og jævnt maskebillede. Garnet er spundet af 100% ren, blød merinould fra får, der ikke har været udsat for mulesing. Et perfekt valg til alt fra bløde babytæpper til chunky sweatre.
                </p>

                <svg class="divider-svg" viewBox="0 0 100 20">
                    <path fill="none" stroke="var(--gold-accent)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" d="M0,10 Q25,20 50,10 T100,10" />
                </svg>

                <div class="specs-grid">
                    <div class="spec-item">
                        <span class="spec-label">Materiale</span>
                        <span class="spec-value">100% Merino Uld</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="spec-item">
                        <span class="spec-label">Løbelængde</span>
                        <span class="spec-value">108m / 50g</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="spec-item">
                        <span class="spec-label">Strikkefasthed</span>
                        <span class="spec-value">20-21 masker / 10 cm</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="spec-item">
                        <span class="spec-label">Vejledende Pinde</span>
                        <span class="spec-value">3.5 - 4.0 mm</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="action-row">
                    <div class="quantity-selector">
                        <button class="qty-btn" onclick="updateQty(-1)">-</button>
                        <input type="number" id="qty-input" class="qty-input" value="1" min="1">
                        <button class="qty-btn" onclick="updateQty(1)">+</button>
                    </div>
                    <button class="btn-add">Reserver til afhentning</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="footer-grid">
            <div class="footer-col">
                <h4>Besøg Butikken</h4>
                <div class="footer-icon-text">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C8.13 2 5 5.13 5 9c0 5.25 7 13 7 13s7-7.75 7-13c0-3.87-3.13-7-7-7zm0 9.5c-1.38 0-2.5-1.12-2.5-2.5s1.12-2.5 2.5-2.5 2.5 1.12 2.5 2.5-1.12 2.5-2.5 2.5z"/></svg>
                    <p>Garnstuen<br>Østerbrogade 138<br>2100 København Ø, DK</p>
                </div>
                <a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Østerbrogade+138,+2100+København+Ø,+Danmark" class="map-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Find Vej</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="footer-col">
                <h4>Kontakt Os</h4>
                <p>Har du brug for hjælp til at finde det rette garn eller matche en strikkefasthed? Skriv direkte til os.</p>
                <a href="https://wa.me/1234567890" class="whatsapp-btn" target="_blank">
